                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210606-172-off993 t18210606-172-cd994"></join>, three shifts, value 4 s.; four petticoats, value 6 d.; four pockets, value 3 s.; one gown, value 10 s.; three aprons, value 1 s.; six handkerchiefs, value 2 s.; one muff, value 2 s.; seven caps, value 4 s.; fourteen collars and frills, value 4 s.; one pair of boots, value 2 s., and two shoes, value 2 s.
