                     <interp inst="t18210606-172-person1735" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I found a bundle at Clifford's, and Collins gave me a muff and other things - I took a cap and handkerchief off the prisoner - she said, the prosecutrix's things were in Corporation-row.</p>
               <p>
            
